c: 19
v: 48
t: "(Abrahamu akaenderera mberi akati): “Ndichashozhonoka (kutarisa rimwe divi kusiri kwamuri baba vangu) kubva kwamuri uye kubva kune izvo zvamunoteketera kunze kwaAllah. Uye (ndichashevedzera) ndichateketera kuna Tenzi vangu (Allah) zvimwe ndingasave mutadzi mukuteketera Tenzi vangu.”"